VALUES (-1580101, 'prophet velen - SAY3', 'The creature Entropius, whom you were forced to destroy, was once the noble naaru, M''uru. In life, M''uru channeled vast energies of LIGHT and HOPE. For a time, a misguided few sought to steal those energies...', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 12518, 0);
